      },
      {
        "step_no": 3,
        "text": "In a medium saucepan combine milk and water and warm over medium heat until it is gently steaming but not boiling.",
        "time_min": 3
      },
      {
        "step_no": 4,
        "text": "Whisk in the semolina slowly in a steady stream to the warm liquid, stirring constantly to prevent lumps. Add the pinch of salt and granulated sugar if using.",
